OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781611874
OL,3,CHistoric Carlisle building set to re-
OL,4,Copen in Bitts Park
OL,6,FAn 'iconic' Carlisle building that has
OL,7,Fbeen closed for more than a decade
OL,8,Fwill reopen, it has been announced.
OL,10,FBitts Park Lodge, which has lain empty
OL,11,Fsince it was damaged during the floods
OL,12,Fof 2015, will be restored for an as-of-
OL,13,Fyet undetermined purpose.
OL,15,FCumberland Council is considering the
OL,16,Ffuture use of Bitts Park Lodge, and
OL,17,Foptions include turning the building
OL,18,Finto a cafe and community hub.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
