FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781611874
OL,3,CHistoric Carlisle building set to re-
OL,4,Copen in Bitts Park
OL,6,FStory Homes and Story Contracting will
OL,7,Ffirst carry out essential repair
OL,8,Fworks, "at no cost to the council", to
OL,9,Fmake the building watertight and
OL,10,Fsecure.
OL,12,FWorks to be tackled include roof
OL,13,Frepairs, new doors and windows and
OL,14,Felectrical and insulation installation.
OL,16,FCarlisle College students will also be
OL,17,Finvited to take part in the
OL,18,Fconstruction, carrying out elements of
OL,19,Ftheir courses on site, and joining
OL,20,Fwork experience programmes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781611874
OL,3,CHistoric Carlisle building set to re-
OL,4,Copen in Bitts Park
OL,6,FCumberland Council said: "Students
OL,7,Fwill gain realworld experience, waste
OL,8,Fwill be significantly reduced, and the
OL,9,Fwork carried out will deliver a
OL,10,Flasting benefit for the local
OL,11,Fcommunity."
OL,13,FLeader of the council, Cllr Mark
OL,14,FFryer, said: "We are delighted that
OL,15,FThe Lodge will once again be open to
OL,16,Fthe public.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
