CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781611874
OL,3,CHistoric Carlisle building set to re-
OL,4,Copen in Bitts Park
OL,6,F"This partnership has the potential to
OL,7,Fshow how the public, private and
OL,8,Feducation sectors can work together in
OL,9,Fdifferent ways to create wider
OL,10,Fcommunity benefits.
OL,12,F"With significant housing pressures
OL,13,Facross Cumberland, this could also be
OL,14,Fan effective way of bringing rundown
OL,15,Fproperties back into use while giving
OL,16,Flocal students invaluable experience."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
