PN,32405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781611874
OL,3,CHistoric Carlisle building set to re-
OL,4,Copen in Bitts Park
OL,6,FSarah McGrath, Principal at Carlisle
OL,7,FCollege, said: "This has the potential
OL,8,Fto be a fantastic opportunity for
OL,9,Fstudents to work on a real project,
OL,10,Fmeet people from across the
OL,11,Fconstruction industry, and even open
OL,12,Fdoors to apprenticeships or work
OL,13,Fexperience.
OL,15,F"It's something they can genuinely
OL,16,Ftake pride in, knowing they played a
OL,17,Fpart in bringing The Lodge back into
OL,18,Fuse."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/5
